    select.SubstraitCompiler.Rd

    dplyr verb implementations

    Usage

    # S3 method for SubstraitCompiler
select(.data, ...)

# S3 method for SubstraitCompiler
rename(.data, ...)

# S3 method for SubstraitCompiler
filter(.data, ...)

# S3 method for SubstraitCompiler
mutate(.data, ...)

# S3 method for SubstraitCompiler
transmute(.data, ...)

# S3 method for SubstraitCompiler
arrange(.data, ...)

# S3 method for SubstraitCompiler
collect(x, ...)

    Arguments

    .data, x

    A substrait_compiler()

    ...

    • select(): see dplyr::select()

      • rename(): see dplyr::rename()

      • filter(): see dplyr::filter()

      • mutate(): see dplyr::mutate()

      • arrange(): see dplyr::arrange()

    Value

    A modified substrait_compiler()
